   Trade Events

   Upcoming Trade Event Highlights. Select this option to view selected
   trade events that are currently being organized by the Office of
   Information Technologies.

   Worldwide Trade Events Listing. Select this option to access a listing
   of IT-related trade events around the world.

   Other Trade Event Resources. Select this option to find out about USA
   Sources (a Chinese-language web site that promotes U.S. IT products) or
   to get links to other trade event databases and web sites.

   Past Trade Events (Results). Select this option to obtain information
   about our past trade events in the Office of Information Technologies.
   * Virtual Trade Mission to China
